name: Franklin stool
description: This comfortable Franklin stool is a reproduction of a classic 1960 design. It is upholstered in top grain leather and features a gentle curve lip on the seat back for extra comfort. The sturdy, solid hardwood frame is available in selection of wood and leather finishes. With a timeless style that pays tribute to original, these highly versatile stools are suitable for residential or commercial use.

name: DeWitt fiberglass shell armchair - eiffel base
description: A and D Modern's DeWitt collection features quality reproductions of the mid-century classic, shell chair design. Available in a wide range of colors, materials, and leg configurations, our DeWitt chairs provide practical seating options for both residential and commercial spaces - from the modern home's dining room or children's bedroom, to the office meeting or waiting room. This fiberglass DeWitt armchair with Eiffel base is true to the original specifications, and is available in a variety of shell seat colors. The polished stainless steel legs with Eiffel-style stainless steel bracing add additional stability to this armchair, while the plastic feet runners protect flooring surfaces from scratching. If you have a specific requirement for a project, we’re happy to help. Please contact one of our professionals to discuss your requirements.
